ActCanada Marine Act
SubjectHamilton-Oshawa Port Authority ** LETTERS PATENT ** **AMENDMENT**
PrecisOrder approving the proposed supplementary LETTERS PATENT provisions in order to increase the aggregate limit on the power of the HAMILTON-OSHAWA PORT AUTHORIRY to borrow money on its credit for port purposes from $45.5 million to $100 million.
